{"tid":700090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本政府跟「特朗普」唱反調: 美韓軍演對東亞安全至關重要","createTime":"2018-06-13T05:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T17:39:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"869eb1c412f1c8ce203b0d58af74ba27d2b0aaa3","tid":700090,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:21:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1865455/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1865455%2F&d=8RTelL83%2BhILtVv%2FCeYAPi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=779af949\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1865455/</a><br />\n<br />\n今日 10:36 時事脈搏<br />\n<br />\n日本稱美韓軍演對東亞安全至關重要<br />\n <br />\n美國總統特朗普昨日在與北韓領導人金正恩會面後，召開記者會，他在記者會上表示，將暫停美韓聯合軍事演習，並希望駐韓美軍回國。美國國防部表示，國防部長馬蒂斯對此不感到意外，事前曾經磋商。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>日本防衞大臣小野寺五典表示，美軍駐守南韓和聯合軍事演習對東亞安全至關重要，日本會繼續和美國舉行聯合軍演，並會堅持加強防衞的計劃，應對可能來自北韓的彈道導彈威脅。</strong><br />\n<br />\n南韓國防部則表示， 首先需要了解特朗普用意何在，截至目前韓美沒有就停止聯合軍演進行過任何磋商，將通過軍事和外交渠道確認特朗普的意圖。"},{"pid":"c58ee4a2dd5d143380f187dbd06d530c5034e233","tid":700090,"uid":59832,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"美韓朝聯合軍演"},{"pid":"a46fee00c7224d6dc2227b7ea9046cffcca2938a","tid":700090,"uid":89931,"like":9,"dislike":18,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:46:48.000Z","msg":"冇人識你呀過主啦"},{"pid":"fbf10d34b579f6dae450aa7ad5a7ff7fbe1f5849","tid":700090,"uid":55990,"like":8,"dislike":18,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:32:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c576a3d1ca4fbb00deefc59531713bb0b7bca53b","tid":700090,"uid":56453,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"咁你地都唔明<br />\n明顯係兩邊一唱一和扯貓尾啦"},{"pid":"b19cd22492944111b620ebfc7c3a39716181b4e8","tid":700090,"uid":14918,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"咁危險, 又真係唔可以取消喎<br />\n<br />\n美韓軍演加埋 日本&amp;北韓<br />\n<br />\n一齊對住中國/俄羅斯軍演啦咁就"},{"pid":"babbffa63f009b15dc70c6fb75fbeab75489197e","tid":700090,"uid":66242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"唔掙在預埋台菲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258049bf7065a669816ca4b2bc37a26b2371074f","tid":700090,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n侵侵唔好走"},{"pid":"f42153bf1082926ec732cd65207d323878e3bf54","tid":700090,"uid":46245,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"咁不如美日韓朝.....再加個台灣聯合軍演啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225320c6cdc29824015f7100d0d3879d5b7870ae","tid":700090,"uid":52215,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/LIeHbhIap44/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FLIeHbhIap44%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=4a4ea09b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c81a3b7fdcc076d21e406155c38031ae6fd755c7","tid":700090,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f42153bf1082926ec732cd65207d323878e3bf54","tid":700090,"uid":46245,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"咁不如美日韓朝.....再加個台灣聯合軍演啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"唔差左溝埋馬來"},{"pid":"6154ca41d030b08746a21d1d087e288fdf960201","tid":700090,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:56:22.000Z","msg":"美日韓朝台聯合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11dd8a69e958afa306ee9ad105911d475ed84a4a","tid":700090,"uid":85456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:01:29.000Z","msg":"屌擺明扯貓尾<im