ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明顯求緊美國繼續駐軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有最強軍隊做保護，果小小保安費抵屌喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://udn.com/news/story/11311/3195457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F11311%2F3195457&d=8RTelL83%2BhILtVv%2FCeYAPi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=fc42c0d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://udn.com/news/story/11311/3195457</a><br />\n<br />\n川普強調，未來將停止「挑釁的」美韓軍演，有朝一日把駐守在南韓的美軍撤回美國。他說：「我想撤離美軍，我想讓軍人回家。只是這不在當前的對等狀態內，我希望它最終可成真。」川普說，撤軍也能為美國省下巨額金錢。"},{"pid":"25f204097c7a53c00e9839f08496ef18b915e5a8","tid":700090,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:18:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43bd81cc7f727e0dd135b90ace899df3b43de3a9","tid":700090,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f99b33edfc71da7d1183ac913b1f73126cca0ea2","tid":700090,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b580fda520b5ba2f6c56e3b26a730312c854075f","tid":700090,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:19:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}